name: Ka-Ching
0:
”Alexa, ask ka ching how much is a bitcoin?”
”Alexa, open ka ching”
”Alexa, ask ka ching what's the current price of a bitcoin?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ka ching
des:
Ka-Ching! will tell you how much one bitcoin is worth in USD.

Disclaimer: The rate is the current market price (spot). Note that exchange rates fluctuates so the price will change every few seconds. The rate will be read aloud and displayed visually (if applicable). The spot price is usually somewhere in between the buy and sell price.

priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
